{"tid":1974111,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"戰神大戰泥馬帶俾我哋嘅啟示","createTime":"2020-04-15T15:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T08:28:39.000Z","uid":89353,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b09c84a549fccd4e5a0c176ce4fb029a26e1c34c","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家睇戰神屌打泥馬係咪好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢用好多terms 係咪好似好勁咁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實你都可以</span></strong><br />\n個重點知唔知係咩<br />\n係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讀書</span></span></strong>呀<br />\n<br />\n好多嘢你睇書花十幾分鐘就可以輕鬆屌打人<br />\n<br />\n物化嗰啲可以睇<br />\n馬克思<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGq4Yvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGq4Yvu.png&h=86c530c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都知你地唔會睇文<br />\n所以我搵埋YouTube比你睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hTK2Za--MGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhTK2Za--MGs&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=e721347d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hTK2Za--MGs</a><br />\n<br />\n（個YouTuber其他嘢都幾多唔同方面嘅知識想學嘢嘅真係可以睇吓）<br />\n<br />\n辯論技巧方面有好多書都有講市面上書局大把<br />\n建議真係睇書<br />\n<br />\n如果YouTube會建議<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJAgfp_jrVTYPY5mPZ9lkiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCJAgfp_jrVTYPY5mPZ9lkiA&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=49b543f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJAgfp_jrVTYPY5mPZ9lkiA</a><br />\n（但佢係台灣人但係用簡體所以⋯都係唔太建議）<br />\n<br />\n講邏輯謬誤嘅可以睇呢本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1Tx7o0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1Tx7o0.jpg&h=239f38b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者睇依個佢都有講<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/JsD6WId1BYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJsD6WId1BYY&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=e41f5ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JsD6WId1BYY</a><br />\n<br />\n之後仲有<br />\n<br />\nttps://youtu.be/MsopuqjbUM4<br />\n入邊都有講到咩叫邏輯謬誤<br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦如果想深入嘅話真係要睇書<br />\n思想嘅話我覺得哲學同基本嘅社會科學應該都要略知一二<br />\n康德丶功利主義丶柏拉圖丶社會契約論呢啲就應該要知下<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有讀書有理性思考有批判性思考先係你同藍絲既分別</span></strong><br />\n幻想下啲藍絲屌你或者你親戚姨媽姑姐屌你<br />\n話你上街係為咗賺外快 公民抗命即係暴徒<br />\n嘅時候你都起碼有返啲理論去支持返自己屌返佢轉頭<br />\n<br />\n奉勸大家一句趁呢個時候讀多啲書<br />\n唔係光復左香港之後 大家都只會係一班人講我就跟嘅新一代藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後光復香港時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：如果真係想研究多啲香港丶民主丶自決既仲有大把書要睇有興趣可以一齊研究吓介紹吓</span>"},{"pid":"237c4625bfa2d77a6b21998369a7708f3e81b3d9","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b47462a03b3869698f92dd0f2bc7e2cbb704af6","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d7af960b6a82e041ac558a5365630e3a444f04","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41710a8c947bb725ada41285f8a65fb173a66f84","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb1a2da659bc6398ea994be92c6a1344d47de32","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21d438a999e