br />\n要唔放棄勸導人學習同思考真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得值得探討下民族主義<br />\n<br />\n民族主義就自然係&quot;想像的共同體&quot;"},{"pid":"f7bdf0eec4396065d5a2d7e792aa221cb5154fc8","tid":1974111,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bc47c197b9f5298353732d22f229224a9aa34e","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc456c1ba336681b92b15571506a7611f789225","tid":1974111,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"睇完大戰 興起翻睇n集哲學有計傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜節目時間有限 講唔到好深入"},{"pid":"8f1d9afa656185191f3558a53d94040d5caa9fba","tid":1974111,"uid":284127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"得閒睇吓"},{"pid":"fad1eaa4cf14cb44eed943b6edde6afe92e50d54","tid":1974111,"uid":212003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"Push, 大家腦袋都要gear up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c4bc95a6ccd25cfa4638866f59fc792fc64aa0","tid":1974111,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:15:03.000Z","msg":"有用post"},{"pid":"cb77b9cbe9fe3b63a25b7096443dc1553dd2ead4","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T21:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95772eb728ff7d8e005cac0b01cf886f26c292c1","tid":1974111,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T21:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"